导航栏

铭轩2023-02-12

类型

interface NavbarItemBasic {
  text: string
  link?: string
  icon?: string
}

interface NavbarItem extends NavbarItemBasic {
  children?: NavbarItemBasic[]
}

type Navbar = NavbarItem[]

TIP

设置图标请参考 指南 -> 图标
